      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can barely stay asleep for more than a couple hours. i already take melatonin every night but it doesnt really seem to be doing much anymore. my doctor gave me some zolpidem (ambien) to help with the insomnia but i was wondering if it's okay to take the melatonin along with it? i figure if i take both it might help them work better together so i can finally get a full night?",
